@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@managerWaId = 5210000000000
@quoteNumber = 12345

### 1) Simular click en template reminder: WF:QUOTED:<folio>
POST {{baseUrl}}/whatsapp/incoming-messages
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "MessageType": "button",
  "WaId": "{{managerWaId}}",
  "Body": "",
  "ButtonPayload": "WF:QUOTED:{{quoteNumber}}",
  "ButtonText": "Ya cotizada"
}

### 2) Responder solo el folio ERP (captura pendiente)
POST {{baseUrl}}/whatsapp/incoming-messages
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "MessageType": "text",
  "WaId": "{{managerWaId}}",
  "Body": "PRO-ERP-77881"
}

### 3) Alternativa directa en un solo mensaje
POST {{baseUrl}}/whatsapp/incoming-messages
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "MessageType": "text",
  "WaId": "{{managerWaId}}",
  "Body": "COTIZADA {{quoteNumber}} PRO-ERP-77881"
}

### 4) Cancelar captura pendiente de folio ERP
POST {{baseUrl}}/whatsapp/incoming-messages
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "MessageType": "text",
  "WaId": "{{managerWaId}}",
  "Body": "CANCELAR"
}

### 5) Simular selección en List Picker (motivo rechazo: No aplica)
POST {{baseUrl}}/whatsapp/incoming-messages
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "MessageType": "interactive",
  "WaId": "{{managerWaId}}",
  "Body": "",
  "ListId": "WF:REJECTED:{{quoteNumber}}:No%20aplica",
  "ListTitle": "No aplica"
}
